Summary: Two star like objects passing over.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Whangarei
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: Sighting DetailsStanding outside my motel room having a coffee, when I spotted a starlike object appearing from above the roof over hang, after a few seconds followed by another one. These objects were traveling in a straight line These passed over at the height off a low flying small plane, but much faster It took me half a a minute or so before I realized that these could not be a plane or helicopter, as no sound was to be heard, and a plane or helicopter has different, or flashing lights The lights were like white light, and so bright that you could not make out a form. As the objects were so low, it only took a couple off minutes before I lost sight off them, behind some houses It was a calm and clear early morning, and I wished I would have had a camera
